            "content": "# Generated by Terraform — MetalLB IP pool for bare-metal LoadBalancer\napiVersion: metallb.io/v1beta1\nkind: IPAddressPool\nmetadata:\n  name: central-pool\n  namespace: metallb-system\nspec:\n  addresses:\n    - 192.168.56.200-192.168.56.220\n---\napiVersion: metallb.io/v1beta1\nkind: L2Advertisement\nmetadata:\n  name: central-l2\n  namespace: metallb-system\nspec:\n  ipAddressPools:\n    - central-pool\n",
